<Base title="Pathfinding — Support" doc>
  <nav><a href="/pathfinding/">← Pathfinding</a></nav>
  <h1>Support</h1>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@sunpebblelabs.com">support@sunpebblelabs.com</a> —
     we usually reply within two days. Or message us on <a href="https://t.me/sunpebble">Telegram</a>.</p>

  <h2>Guest mode vs. account</h2>
  <p>You can plan as a guest — your trips stay on the device only. Sign in (email or Apple) if you want
     trips synced across devices; then your trips are stored with your account.</p>

  <h2>Syncing trips</h2>
  <p>Sign in on another device with the same account and your trips appear after a moment. If a trip
     doesn't show, pull to refresh or reopen the app.</p>

  <h2>Deleting your account</h2>
  <p>Open Profile → settings to delete your account and its data. This can't be undone. See the
     <a href="/pathfinding/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
</Base>
